        {
            "title": "中信銀行2025年業績快報：純利按年升2.98%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">中信銀行(00998)發表2025年度業績快報，顯示根據中國會計準則，去年歸屬銀行股東淨利潤706.18億元(人民幣．下同)，按年微升2.98%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"Shutterstock圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20230824_FI_source_licensed_00998_shutterstock_.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"Shutterstock圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20230824_FI_source_licensed_00998_shutterstock_.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">Shutterstock圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">期內營業總收入約2127.74億元，則較2024年度減少0.55%。營業利潤836.74億元，按年增長3.39%；利潤總額840.43億元，也增長3.93%。歸屬銀行股東並扣除非經常性損益的淨利潤為98.19億元，按年增長2.58%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">截至去年底，中信銀行不良貸款率1.15%，比2024年底下降0.01個百分點；撥備覆蓋率203.61%，按年下降5.82個百分點。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15582337-%e4%b8%ad%e4%bf%a1%e9%8a%80%e8%a1%8c2025%e5%b9%b4%e6%a5%ad%e7%b8%be%e5%bf%ab%e5%a0%b1%ef%bc%9a%e7%b4%94%e5%88%a9%e6%8c%89%e5%b9%b4%e5%8d%872-98",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/08/20230824_FI_source_licensed_00998_shutterstock_fb.png.webp",
